{"word":"G1222 - δήπου - dḗpou - day'-poo - Verily","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δήπου</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">dḗpou</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">day'-poo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Verily</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஆதலால் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"now in some way, whatever that way is"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1211 - δή - dḗ - day/1211\">G1211</a> and <a href=\"#/G4225 - πού - poú - poo/4225\">G4225</a>; a particle of asseveration; <i>indeed doubtless:</i> - verily.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}